cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper deals with vision-based motion estimation and robotics, which are typically covered under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of deep learning models (cs.LG) and probabilistic regression (cs.AI) to estimate rotations. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of learned covariances to improve localization, which falls under the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
